    "date": "2021-08-23T16:06:53Z",
    "text": "Secure United States Bases Act\n\nThis bill revises requirements related to U.S.-based foreign military training programs. Specifically, the bill\n\n creates a visa category for certain aliens who have been accepted into a U.S.-based military training program; adds application, vetting, and monitoring requirements for foreign military trainees; and requires the Department of Defense to develop a method for classifying the relative risk, by country, of accepting foreign personnel into U.S. military training programs."
  },
